productAttributes.productDescription: Ceiling fans, although quite useful, are hardly enough to beat the sweltering heat of summer. productAttributes.title: Symphony Diet 22i Tower Air Cooler
productAttributes.productDescription: Does the thought of having stale air circulating in your house prevent you from installing an AC? While a ceiling fan alone is not enough in summer, this Symphony air cooler will make summer in your house less hotter and will also ensure that you are breathing fresh air. With a high-efficiency honeycomb cooling pad and a powerful blower, this cooler works on evaporative cooling technology, thus absorbing heat by evaporating water so the air circulated in your house is fresh and pure. Water Tank With A Capacity Of 22 Liters The water tank in this air cooler has a capacity of 22 liters, so you can enjoy uninterrupted cooling. The water tank also has an alarm that beeps to remind you when the water level is low. The pump gets turned off when the water level is low, thus preventing any damage to your air cooler. The drain plug at the bottom lets you remove residual water from the water tank. Dura-Pump Technology This cooler is designed with the Dura-Pump technology, making the water pump strong and durable, thus giving your air cooler a long life. Works On Inverter Power Frequent power cuts are not going to leave you sweating and irritable in your house as this Symphony air cooler also works on inverter power. Powerful Air Throw This air cooler has a powerful blower with an auto swing function, giving you a superior multi-directional air throw. You can modify the level of air throw by using the adjustable vertical louver. Includes Mosquito Net And Dust Filter With a mosquito net and a dust filter, the cooler ensures that the air that enters your house is fresh and hygienic. Ideal For Outdoor And Indoor Use With your Symphony tower air cooler, you can enjoy summer mornings in your garden, basking in fresh air as you relax on your hammock. Includes A Remote Control The cooler comes with a remote control so you can operate it without having to get up from the couch. The cooler also has a dock on which you can place the remote to look neat when you leave the house.
